          {
            "title": "Code block",
            "id": 75857,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>  As declarações <code>if</code> não decidem pular ou executar o código <em>inteiro</em>. Elas apenas tomam decisões sobre um <strong>bloco de código</strong>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;I'm a code block!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"11\" endIndex=\"37\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"I'm a code block!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>print(\"I'm a code block!\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Code block",
            "id": 76082,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Usamos uma <strong>indentação de dois espaços</strong> para destacar blocos de código, como indentar esta instrução de exibição.<br /></p><p><strong>Indentação</strong> refere-se ao espaço entre o código e a margem do editor de código.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;I'm two spaces away!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"11\" endIndex=\"40\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"I'm two spaces away!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>print(\"I'm two spaces away!\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Code block",
            "id": 75855,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Um bloco de código pode ter mais de uma linha. Todas as linhas com a mesma indentação pertencem ao mesmo bloco de código.</p><p>Podemos ver isso aqui quando usamos <code>print()</code> para adicionar mais uma linha no início.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Look at me!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;I'm a code block&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"11\" endIndex=\"16\" /><option startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"30\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Look at me!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"I'm a code block\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>print</code> seguido de <code>\"Look at me!\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Indentation Error",
            "id": 124593,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Se a indentação estiver incorreta, o computador não consegue entender o seu código. Isso leva a um <code>IndentationError</code> aparecendo no console.</p><p>Aqui, o segundo <code>print()</code> está com a indentação errada por apenas um espaço em vez de dois, como o primeiro <code>print()</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Look at me!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;I'm a code block&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"33\" endIndex=\"38\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"  File &quot;/home/default/code/file.py&quot;, line 3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(&quot;I'm a code block&quot;)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"                             ^\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"IndentationError: unindent does not match any outer indentation level\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>print</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "True Variable",
            "id": 75850,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Em vez de usar o booleano <code>True</code>, podemos salvá-lo em uma variável como <code>greet</code> e usá-lo como a condição.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"greet = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greet:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"21\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>greet</code>.</p></body></html>"
